casebody.data:
JILANI
v.
HARRISON 139P17-2 Supreme Court of North Carolina. July 6, 2017 Mohammed Nasser Jilani, for Jilani, Mohammed Nasser. Daniel P. O'Brien, Special Deputy Attorney General, N. Lorrin Freeman, District Attorney, for State of N.C.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 6th of July 2017 by Petitioner for Application for Enforcement of Writ sec. 17-16 Attachment for Failure to Obey:

"Motion Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 6th of July 2017."
